chess chessBoard game:
requirements:

1) chess game
chessBoard and pieces and 2 players game
2) turn one after another
3) checkmate then game over
4) keep track of the pieces and chessBoard to avoid the illegal move
5) keep track of the current positions of all the boxes and pieces

Design classes and relationships
write down all the entities
chessBoard, game, chessPlayer, piece

chessBoard class should keep track of all the cells

